---
import LocationLayout from '../layouts/LocationLayout.astro';

const content = `
<h2>Professional Mobile Car Detailing in St. Petersburg, FL</h2>
<p>St. Petersburg is known for its sunshine — and that same sunshine is constantly working against your vehicle's finish. Shine For Christ Mobile Auto Detailing provides professional mobile car detailing throughout St. Petersburg, from downtown to the beaches and everywhere in between. We come to your location so you don't have to go anywhere.</p>

<p>Our mobile detailing service is built for convenience. Whether you're at home in Old Northeast, at work near the Gateway area, or parked at your condo downtown, we bring all the equipment and supplies needed for a full professional detail. No shop visit, no waiting room, no wasted time.</p>

<h3>Protecting Your Vehicle in the Sunshine City</h3>
<p>St. Petersburg averages more than 360 days of sunshine per year, which means constant UV exposure for your vehicle. Over time, this leads to paint oxidation, faded trim, cracked leather, and cloudy headlights. Our detailing services are designed to both restore and protect — removing existing damage while applying protective coatings that shield your finish from the elements.</p>

<p>Coastal salt air is another factor that St. Pete drivers deal with daily. Salt accelerates corrosion and can pit chrome and metal surfaces. Regular professional detailing removes salt deposits and applies protective barriers that keep your vehicle looking sharp and structurally sound.</p>

<h3>Detailing Services for St. Petersburg Residents</h3>
<p>We offer comprehensive mobile detailing packages in St. Petersburg, including exterior wash and wax, clay bar treatment, paint correction, ceramic coating, interior deep cleaning, leather care, carpet extraction, and more. Every package can be customized with add-ons to address your vehicle's specific needs.</p>

<p>From classic cars in the Garage Mahals to daily commuters on I-275, Shine For Christ provides the same meticulous attention to detail for every vehicle we touch. <a href="/contact" class="text-primary font-semibold hover:underline">Give us a call</a> and let us bring a showroom shine to your St. Petersburg vehicle.</p>
`;
